    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《不思议林中漫游》是一款以少女为主角的平台跳跃解谜游戏，你将在旅途中遇见可爱的伙伴与萌趣的生物，或者用不可思议的力量解开奇妙的谜题！化身少女踏入变幻的四季，来找到拯救野森的方法吧！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/f3fab42692a98aed6e37a40f9027b03f.poster.avif?t=1771411721\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/f3fab42692a98aed6e37a40f9027b03f.webm?t=1771411721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/f3fab42692a98aed6e37a40f9027b03f.mp4?t=1771411721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个好奇心满满的可爱女孩，眨眼间就跌进了一个闪闪发光、温暖梦幻的童话世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，各种柔软的小可爱，害羞躲藏的小动物，与大大的兔子等待着少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在与他们建立的羁绊里，在这场奇妙的漫游中，少女将解决谜题，也将感受到成长的温暖与治愈。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/d5c7e0eb71bda5cc9690101f34e08bd7.poster.avif?t=1771411721\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/d5c7e0eb71bda5cc9690101f34e08bd7.webm?t=1771411721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/d5c7e0eb71bda5cc9690101f34e08bd7.mp4?t=1771411721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想不想成为重塑地平线的少女？最最最最不可思议的力量来啦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >转转转，摆摆摆，传送门随你来使用！上一秒，站在这里，下一秒，出现在天边。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者掌握时机，改变一切的重力方向，让时间与空间碰撞，产生奇妙的新变化。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/4bc8e258103ba902eab1d93b73df1c6f.poster.avif?t=1771411721\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/4bc8e258103ba902eab1d93b73df1c6f.webm?t=1771411721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173210/extras/4bc8e258103ba902eab1d93b73df1c6f.mp4?t=1771411721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在路途上领略四季独特的领域，它们各有各的环境、生命与谜题，美好的风光与遇见等待着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来吧，一起在这片森林中静静漫步，悠然探索周围的每个角落，这段旅程将轻松治愈，却处处藏着细节与心意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站：@不思议林中漫游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小黑盒：@不思议林中漫游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小红书：@不思议林中漫游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【加入愿望单！和少女一起冒险！】</p>",
